description: Mmmm... Mad Grill…LEAN MEAN PAN-ASIAN CUISINE! A head turner and a stomach grumbler passing you in traffic. Mad Grill Pan-Asian Fusion Food Truck is cruising the streets of the DFW area offering a fusion of your favorite dishes from all over Asia. Check out the spring rolls and pork buns, or create your own dish from a wide array of bases, rice, and meats or veggies! Stop by and grab a bite!
name: Mad Grill
